# Master Plan Protocol

## Active Phase

**Current phase: Complete through Phase 6**
**Phase brief: `docs/plans/phase-6-brief.md`**
**Master plan: `docs/plans/master-plan.md`**

## Before Modifying Any File

1. Check the file ownership matrix below. If the file belongs to another workstream, do NOT modify it unless the matrix says you may.
2. Read the current phase brief (`docs/plans/phase-6-brief.md`) before starting work.
3. All planned phases through 6 are complete. New work should be scoped from follow-up directives or deferred backlog items in `docs/plans/master-plan.md`.

## File Ownership Matrix

| File / Area | Owner | Others May... |
|---|---|---|
| `supabase/migrations/*_market_stats*` | Reporting | Not touch |
| `app/actions/market-stats.ts` | Reporting | Import and call |
| `app/api/cron/sync-full/route.ts` | Reporting | Not touch |
| `components/reports/*` | Reporting | Import and render |
| `app/housing-market/*` | Reporting | Monetization adds AdUnit slots |
| `app/search/[...slug]/page.tsx` section order | Engagement | Monetization adds ad slots + route segments |
| `app/page.tsx` section order | Engagement | Monetization adds ad slots |
| `app/listing/[listingKey]/page.tsx` sections | Engagement | Monetization adds ad slots |
| `app/actions/activity-feed.ts` | Engagement | Not touch |
| `components/PageCTA.tsx` | Engagement | Not touch |
| `components/AdUnit.tsx` | Monetization | Others don't touch |
| `app/layout.tsx` (site-wide banner) | Monetization | Engagement doesn't add global UI |
| `app/sitemap.ts` | Monetization | Reporting may add report URLs |
| `app/guides/*` | Monetization | Not touch |
| `lib/followupboss.ts` | Shared | Extend carefully, don't break existing |
| `components/ShareButton.tsx` | Shared | Extend carefully |
| `app/admin/*` | Admin | Only superuser changes |

## After Completing Work

1. Mark completed tasks in the phase brief (change `[ ]` to `[x]`).
2. When all tasks in a phase are done, update this rule: change the active phase number and phase brief path.
3. Create the next phase brief (`docs/plans/phase-N-brief.md`) from the master plan.

## Key Constraints

- **SEO is a gate**: every phase must pass the SEO verification checklist in the master plan before shipping.
- **Reporting data layer is the single source of truth**: use `getCachedStats()` and `getLiveMarketPulse()` from `app/actions/market-stats.ts`. Do NOT use old `getCityMarketStats()`.
- **Lead capture stacking**: StickyMobileCTA and SiteLeadCaptureBanner must not both be visible simultaneously.
- **Ad slot order on listing detail**: existing sections → AreaMarketContext → AdUnit → Similar Listings → ActivityFeedSlider → RecentlySoldRow → sidebar ad below CTA.
- **Filter page links**: Browse-by UI components link to Monetization's `/search/{city}/{filter}` routes, not query-param URLs.
- **`npm run build` must pass** before any work is considered complete.
